/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毛魔講過：人民、只有人民，才是創造世界歷史的動力。<br />\n如果下下行易行既路，選擇依靠權貴<br />\n世界是不會有進步<br />\n所以現在香港人的性格怕改變才是要改的地方"},{"pid":"75a883285f5b4dfd7bb7ba6a2d89a38e4d831e04","tid":388544,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:00:26.000Z","msg":"改打破困境從來唔會靠政府<br />\n反而係大眾的意志"},{"pid":"8ca8f1aa93759f98123854f2915118cdadfbf8a9","tid":388544,"uid":92628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"要打倒地產商，以為增加供應就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟樓主了解地產商幾多？ 知已知彼，連敵人係咩都唔知，何來打倒。改變世界唔係靠幾句漂亮話就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好簡單，樓主知唔知地產商有邊幾個，市值幾多，業務有幾多，政府權益有幾多，回報有幾多，唔知就番去做下research先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d028d65f21f2db61bc29cdce08dcd32b506d65","tid":388544,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要打倒地產商，以為增加供應就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟樓主了解地產商幾多？ 知已知彼，連敵人係咩都唔知，何來打倒。改變世界唔係靠幾句漂亮話就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好簡單，樓主知唔知地產商有邊幾個，市值幾多，業務有幾多，政府權益有幾多，回報有幾多，唔知就番去做下research先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n增加左先講啦"},{"pid":"3abce8506394c40bf91799fedbb3da135edb53dc","tid":388544,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e62afae45f38b1051550b33ce36d7fb94169ec1","tid":388544,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}